    </div><!-- END .sixteen.columns -->

    <div class="row">
      <div class="left_half columns">
        <dl>
          <dt>Is HookFeed Secure?</dt>
          <dd>Completely. When you connect HookFeed to your Stripe account you’re giving us read-only access. All interactions within the app are SSL encrypted. And we’ll never share your information with anyone.</dd>

          <dt>Can I cancel anytime?</dt>
          <dd>Yes. We’ll be sad to see you go, but if HookFeed isn’t for you we totally understand. We make it super easy to cancel your service and disconnect your Stripe account.</dd>

          <dt>Which Stripe events do you track?</dt>
          <dd>Currently we track Charges, Failed Charges, Refunds, New Subscribers, Cancellations, Bank Transfers, Failed Bank Transfers, Disputed Charges, and Settled Disputes. We are open to your suggestions for other events. A full list of events from Stripe can be found <a href="https://stripe.com/docs/api#list_events">here</a>.</dd>
        </dl>
      </div><!-- END .left_half.columns -->

      <div class="right_half columns">
        <dl>

          <dt>Do I need to know how to code?</dt>
          <dd>No! You can connect your Stripe account to HookFeed in one click. Literally. No code necessary.</dd>

          <dt>Can I pick what events get sent to me?</dt>
          <dd>Yes. Once you’re logged into your HookFeed account you can choose which events get sent to you in an instant email alert, and which events will be compiled into a daily and/or weekly digest email. You'll do the same for any teammates you add.</dd>

